ers, those studying and teaching journalism, and avid consumers of the media will be interested in this book.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Mai 2022) 7aLANGUAGE ARTS & DISCIPLINES / Journalism.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022 Englishz978311099389908iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022z9783110994810oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Library and Information Science 2022 Englishz978311099318908iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Library and Information Science 2022z9783110993103oZDB-23-DGB08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertPenn State University Press Complete eBook-Package 2022z978311076692940uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978027109262140uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780271092621423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780271092621/original  a978-3-11-076692-9  Penn State University Press Complete eBook-Package 2022b2022  a978-3-11-099318-9  EBOOK PACKAGE Library and Information Science 2022 Englishb2022  a978-3-11-099389-9  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022 Englishb2022  aEBA_CL_LB  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_LB  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGBb2022  aZDB-23-DGGb2022